import React from 'react'
import Back from '../common/back/Back'
import AboutCard from './AboutCard'
import Header from '../common/heading/Header'

const About = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <Back title='About Us' />
      <AboutCard />

    </>
  )
}

export default About
